{"tid":2318513,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尋人: 熱心人證侯先生 26/11 7:00pm 美孚站幫手捉人偷拍","createTime":"2020-12-09T11:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T12:35:37.000Z","uid":67866,"like":50,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ea90eb0a3add8202e1b3f09a32deb0debc654536","tid":2318513,"uid":67866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T11:24:04.000Z","msg":"各位手足幫個忙<br />\n<br />\n事源 26/11 大概夜晚7點係美孚站有位手足見到有人偷拍女仔幫手捉到, 手足侯先生當時陪我地同黑警交代件事，都有留低資料俾黑警，最後想息事寧人冇告到話，用黨鐵附例罰錢算數。<br />\n當時侯先生走個陣冇留到contact，點知黑警困咗我地係房3個鐘先話黨鐵附例告唔入，不如就咁算，咁我地梗係告啦<br />\n拖到今日終於約到落口供，但係黑警就係咁話聯絡唔到證人侯先生一齊落口供，話唔信佢地係警察，真心痴撚線。依家由於我地冇留到contact真係任9佢地噏，所以係度拜託各位手足幫手尋下人<br />\n我地真係好需要搵番侯先生<br />\n<br />\n或者侯先生睇到個post可以聯絡96509880<br />\n麻煩晒各位手足🥲🥲"},{"pid":"70f0278b264844e02aac59f1cb9ea035b21d23d6","tid":2318513,"uid":24820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T11:29:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38396f363c8a5b90b0be7ceb0ca4b6f345ed3bba","tid":2318513,"uid":161350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T11:30:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da7e256474054cc1fcc3e0c69d12228d29690c22","tid":2318513,"uid":67866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T11:32:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55f8e30f037aa495c4bf23bbdcf83ef323db7ab7","tid":2318513,"uid":169819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T11:32:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efcde43673cf2c954c2b0f2b135f88e443b2f20d","tid":2318513,"uid":67866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T11:33:20.000Z","msg":"感謝手足幫手推🙇&zwj;♂️🙇&zwj;♂️🙇&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"9f6cfccb763d67b95fbb515a41b98638c75821c5","tid":2318513,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T11:34:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c29bad5ecaffed8f18d53ea026fb2dc97a5117a","tid":2318513,"uid":135927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T11:35:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c3bb88fc1c176fd575bed6744dc430550505ab8